title: Week 9 Matchups + Wheel of Shame - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/5
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode to help you get a win in Week 9! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Week 9 matchup breakdowns, injury updates, and more! Plus, a recap of the Colts vs Jets game, and a new edition of “Fantasy Faceoff” with the Wheel of Shame! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 5th, 2021.
  
 (04:45) - FootClan Friday
 (05:40) - Thursday Night Recap
 (12:55) - NFL News
 (26:55) - Fantasy Forecast
 (27:25) - Bills at Jaguars
 (31:45) - Vikings at Ravens
 (36:50) - Chargers at Eagles
 (42:15) - Packers at Chiefs
 (46:10) - Cardinals at 49ers
 (51:10) - Titans at Rams
 (56:25) - Bears at Steelers
 (01:00:45) - Fantasy Faceoff + Wheel of Shame
